      "body" : "@cyberluke bitcoin-cli is a completely separate program from bitcoind. It can't possibly know whether you modified the bitcoin.conf while bitcoind was running. This is not \"bad file handling design\", there's just no other way for bitcoin-cli to know the rpcuser and password unless you explicitly give it those parameters.",
